<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="12Sep1936"><font color="red">12 September 1936</font> <i>NLJL</i> (from John Lane to Paul L&eacute;on): This is to confirm &hellip; that we have safely received all answers to our queries; also that we have no further queries and that the complete text has now been composed. We are now waiting to hear from Mr Joyce about the Appendix material, proofs of which were sent to him by me to the Hamburg address on Thursday. (10 September 1936) </div>
